===Verb===
{{en-verb|spot|t|ing}}

#<!--VTrNotice--> {{transitive}} to [[see]], [[find]]; to [[pick out]], [[notice]] or [[identify]] <!-- could STILL be improved --> <!-- somehow similar to "locate"? -->
#:''Try to '''spot''' the differences between these two entries.''
#<!--VTrloan--> {{finance}} to [[loan]] [[money]] to somebody
#: ''I'll '''spot''' you three dollars.''
#<!--VTrCreateStain-->to stain; to leave a spot
#:''Hard water will '''spot''' if it is left on a surface.''
#<!--VTrRemoveStain-->to remove, or attempt to remove, a stain
#:''I '''spotted''' the carpet where the child dropped spaghetti.''
#<!--VTrAssist--> (''gymnastics'') & {{weightlifting}}: to [[support]] or [[assist]] a maneuver, or to be prepared to assist if safety dictates
#:''I can't do a back handspring unless somebody '''spots''' me.''
#<!--VInFocusOnePoint--> (''dance'') to keep the head and eyes pointing in a single direction while [[turn]]ing
#:''Most figure skaters do not '''spot''' their turns like dancers do.''

